audios.name: 但这种小场面贝爷根本...
使整个人牢牢卡在缝隙...
贝爷化掌为拳卡在缝隙...
光是之前的极限攀爬运...
没办法只能重新包裹好...
但是担心里面藏着美杜...
当务之急还是寻找淡水...
还真让他瞎猫碰到死耗...
毫无疑问是正宗的野生...

texts.content: {"styles":[{"fill":{"alpha":1.0,"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"alpha":1.0,"color":[1.0,1.0,1.0]}}},"font":{"id":"","path":"C:/Users/27919/AppData/Local/JianyingPro/Apps/5.4.0.11246/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf"},"range":[0,17],"size":5.0}],"text":"穿过水下乱石区，也不知具体游了多久"}

{"styles":[{"fill":{"alpha":1.0,"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"alpha":1.0,"color":[1.0,1.0,1.0]}}},"font":{"id":"","path":"C:/Users/27919/AppData/Local/JianyingPro/Apps/5.4.0.11246/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf"},"range":[0,18],"size":5.0}],"text":"等贝爷再次漏头，已经累得上气不接下气"}

{"styles":[{"fill":{"alpha":1.0,"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"alpha":1.0,"color":[1.0,1.0,1.0]}}},"font":{"id":"","path":"C:/Users/27919/AppData/Local/JianyingPro/Apps/5.4.0.11246/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf"},"range":[0,21],"size":5.0}],"text":"这下不仅水没有喝到，还损失了几头牛的蛋白质"}

{"styles":[{"fill":{"alpha":1.0,"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"alpha":1.0,"color":[1.0,1.0,1.0]}}},"font":{"id":"","path":"C:/Users/27919/AppData/Local/JianyingPro/Apps/5.4.0.11246/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf"},"range":[0,15],"size":5.0}],"text":"意识到此地不已久留，刚打算逃离"}

{"styles":[{"fill":{"alpha":1.0,"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"alpha":1.0,"color":[1.0,1.0,1.0]}}},"font":{"id":"","path":"C:/Users/27919/AppData/Local/JianyingPro/Apps/5.4.0.11246/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf"},"range":[0,22],"size":5.0}],"text":"前方竟是一处死胡同，真是小刀拉屁股--开了眼"}

{"styles":[{"fill":{"alpha":1.0,"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"alpha":1.0,"color":[1.0,1.0,1.0]}}},"font":{"id":"","path":"C:/Users/27919/AppData/Local/JianyingPro/Apps/5.4.0.11246/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf"},"range":[0,15],"size":5.0}],"text":"但这种小场面贝爷根本没放在心上"}

{"styles":[{"fill":{"alpha":1.0,"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"alpha":1.0,"color":[1.0,1.0,1.0]}}},"font":{"id":"","path":"C:/Users/27919/AppData/Local/JianyingPro/Apps/5.4.0.11246/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf"},"range":[0,22],"size":5.0}],"text":"对付这种路线，最好采取烟囱攀登法，借助脚和背"}

{"styles":[{"fill":{"alpha":1.0,"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"alpha":1.0,"color":[1.0,1.0,1.0]}}},"font":{"id":"","path":"C:/Users/27919/AppData/Local/JianyingPro/Apps/5.4.0.11246/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf"},"range":[0,22],"size":5.0}],"text":"使整个人牢牢卡在缝隙里，通过手掌提供的摩擦力"}

{"styles":[{"fill":{"alpha":1.0,"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"alpha":1.0,"color":[1.0,1.0,1.0]}}},"font":{"id":"","path":"C:/Users/27919/AppData/Local/JianyingPro/Apps/5.4.0.11246/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf"},"range":[0,16],"size":5.0}],"text":"腰马合一向上挪动，过程说起来容易"}

{"styles":[{"fill":{"alpha":1.0,"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"alpha":1.0,"color":[1.0,1.0,1.0]}}},"font":{"id":"","path":"C:/Users/27919/AppData/Local/JianyingPro/Apps/5.4.0.11246/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf"},"range":[0,19],"size":5.0}],"text":"没有几年的攀岩经验，很难把控其中的细节"}

{"styles":[{"fill":{"alpha":1.0,"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"alpha":1.0,"color":[1.0,1.0,1.0]}}},"font":{"id":"","path":"C:/Users/27919/AppData/Local/JianyingPro/Apps/5.4.0.11246/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf"},"range":[0,22],"size":5.0}],"text":"眼看即将登顶，又被一块巨石挡住，找不到着力点"}

{"styles":[{"fill":{"alpha":1.0,"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"alpha":1.0,"color":[1.0,1.0,1.0]}}},"font":{"id":"","path":"C:/Users/27919/AppData/Local/JianyingPro/Apps/5.4.0.11246/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf"},"range":[0,20],"size":5.0}],"text":"贝爷化掌为拳卡在缝隙，以此为锚点带动身体"}

{"styles":[{"fill":{"alpha":1.0,"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"alpha":1.0,"color":[1.0,1.0,1.0]}}},"font":{"id":"","path":"C:/Users/27919/AppData/Local/JianyingPro/Apps/5.4.0.11246/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf"},"range":[0,19],"size":5.0}],"text":"好家伙，简直是小母牛坐飞机，牛*上天了"}

{"styles":[{"fill":{"alpha":1.0,"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"alpha":1.0,"color":[1.0,1.0,1.0]}}},"font":{"id":"","path":"C:/Users/27919/AppData/Local/JianyingPro/Apps/5.4.0.11246/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf"},"range":[0,19],"size":5.0}],"text":"重返炎炎烈日下，贝爷一时竟不知如何是好"}

{"styles":[{"fill":{"alpha":1.0,"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"alpha":1.0,"color":[1.0,1.0,1.0]}}},"font":{"id":"","path":"C:/Users/27919/AppData/Local/JianyingPro/Apps/5.4.0.11246/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf"},"range":[0,23],"size":5.0}],"text":"光是之前的极限攀爬运动下来就损失掉大几千卡能量"}

{"styles":[{"fill":{"alpha":1.0,"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"alpha":1.0,"color":[1.0,1.0,1.0]}}},"font":{"id":"","path":"C:/Users/27919/AppData/Local/JianyingPro/Apps/5.4.0.11246/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf"},"range":[0,25],"size":5.0}],"text":"没办法只能重新包裹好头套，找准备先找个阴凉地冷静下"}

{"styles":[{"fill":{"alpha":1.0,"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"alpha":1.0,"color":[1.0,1.0,1.0]}}},"font":{"id":"","path":"C:/Users/27919/AppData/Local/JianyingPro/Apps/5.4.0.11246/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf"},"range":[0,23],"size":5.0}],"text":"跋涉将近一个钟，岩缝下的洞穴吸引了贝爷的注意力"}

{"styles":[{"fill":{"alpha":1.0,"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"alpha":1.0,"color":[1.0,1.0,1.0]}}},"font":{"id":"","path":"C:/Users/27919/AppData/Local/JianyingPro/Apps/5.4.0.11246/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf"},"range":[0,23],"size":5.0}],"text":"但是担心里面藏着美杜莎，贝子先扔几块石头探一探"}

{"styles":[{"fill":{"alpha":1.0,"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"alpha":1.0,"color":[1.0,1.0,1.0]}}},"font":{"id":"","path":"C:/Users/27919/AppData/Local/JianyingPro/Apps/5.4.0.11246/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf"},"range":[0,12],"size":5.0}],"text":"消除顾虑后，才敢躺下休息"}

{"styles":[{"fill":{"alpha":1.0,"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"alpha":1.0,"color":[1.0,1.0,1.0]}}},"font":{"id":"","path":"C:/Users/27919/AppData/Local/JianyingPro/Apps/5.4.0.11246/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf"},"range":[0,20],"size":5.0}],"text":"时间来到第二天，油条包子，胡辣汤统统没吃"}

{"styles":[{"fill":{"alpha":1.0,"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"alpha":1.0,"color":[1.0,1.0,1.0]}}},"font":{"id":"","path":"C:/Users/27919/AppData/Local/JianyingPro/Apps/5.4.0.11246/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf"},"range":[0,21],"size":5.0}],"text":"当务之急还是寻找淡水，利用清晨周围的虫鸣声"}

{"styles":[{"fill":{"alpha":1.0,"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"alpha":1.0,"color":[1.0,1.0,1.0]}}},"font":{"id":"","path":"C:/Users/27919/AppData/Local/JianyingPro/Apps/5.4.0.11246/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf"},"range":[0,18],"size":5.0}],"text":"贝爷一路追踪下陡坡，来到声源密集位置"}

{"styles":[{"fill":{"alpha":1.0,"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"alpha":1.0,"color":[1.0,1.0,1.0]}}},"font":{"id":"","path":"C:/Users/27919/AppData/Local/JianyingPro/Apps/5.4.0.11246/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf"},"range":[0,22],"size":5.0}],"text":"还真让他瞎猫碰到死耗子，找到一处湿漉漉的岩缝"}

{"styles":[{"fill":{"alpha":1.0,"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"alpha":1.0,"color":[1.0,1.0,1.0]}}},"font":{"id":"","path":"C:/Users/27919/AppData/Local/JianyingPro/Apps/5.4.0.11246/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf"},"range":[0,16],"size":5.0}],"text":"毫无疑问是正宗的野生山泉渗出的水"}
